Name: Alfredo812
Title: Serene
Review: This is a lovely temple. Very clean, maintained, peaceful, and the aura here is just amazing! A must visit no matter what.

Name: Ramandeep M
Title: Perfect
Review: Enjoyed my visit to this monastery.Located in Spituk and found very useful information from people living there. If yuu have time, its a must visit monastery.

Name: Ajay R
Title: A heavenly feeling amidst nature
Review: This is a legend and if you are in Ladakh, one must not miss this . It is located amidst nature and offering prayers gives you a feeling of inner peace which is unparalled to any other materialistic aspects . Not to be missed for sure

Name: Geetuppal
Title: Kali Ma
Review: Kali mata mandir . is one of the most beautiful temples set in the hills of Leh , it is on top of a hill where the view is just lovely and i can say is jannat . A must visit to a beautiful Temple .
